 moons could be with an instrumental transit sensitivity of\n$10^{-5}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2020 16:22:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Apr 2021 12:38:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-29"}
