To demonstrate the power of the rephasing we also conducted quite\na few numerical experiments, compared the results we obtained through them to\nthe theoretical predictions, and observed an excellent agreement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2020 16:36:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-24"}
