eck all of them,\ndue to the lack of available experimental results over a broad temperature\nrange.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2020 18:16:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Dec 2020 05:15:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-17"}
