ving our solution, we design\nthe first data structure for addressing a special instance of circular sector\nemptiness queries among polyhedral obstacles in three dimensional space, and\nprovide a simplified data structure for the corresponding emptiness query\nproblem in two dimensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2020 19:24:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-25"}
