 tube still functions well, maintaining a low\nemissivity and good vacuum after approximately 40 years in storage conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2020 10:43:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Apr 2021 00:06:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 26 Mar 2022 00:34:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-29"}
