ly. We verify these hypotheses in several\nexamples. We finally compare our measures of disorder with several disorder\npredictors, showing that these latter are optimized to predict the residues\nthat are missing in all the alternative structures of a protein, and they are\nnot able to catch the progressive evolution of the disordered regions upon\ncomplex formation. Yet, the predicted residues, if not missing, tend to be\ncharacterized as soft disordered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2020 10:59:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-01"}
